{"tid":1911362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主黨請願不滿通訊局容許免費電視台毋須播放 港台節目","createTime":"2020-03-05T09:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T10:01:36.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"270be9c69dd3cb0c9a3f467c70a19faad170ef00","tid":1911362,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"民主黨到通訊事務管理局辦公室請願，不滿通訊局容許免費電視台毋須播放香港電台節目，要求通訊局向免費電視台，收取「頻譜使用費」。請願人士高叫「捍衞言論自由」及「港台加油」的口號。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨深水埗區議員袁海文說，港台已非首次受到「陰乾」，以往通訊局已經容許無綫電視毋須播放城市論壇，今次又再容許免費電視台毋須播放港台節目。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員鄺俊宇說，相信香港人已經養成「轉台」文化，即使免費電視台不再轉播港台節目，觀眾亦會自行收看港台電視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1512639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1512639&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=e2cb0288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1512639&h=39ed5645\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1512639</a>"},{"pid":"8677cd7e99d565db1c4266cf57f6aceb79cd702a","tid":1911362,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFM58x6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFM58x6.jpg&h=6f72f7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1fbjEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1fbjEM.jpg&h=33504ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8Mar #將軍澳 #悼念會 #周同學<br />\n【梓樂悼念會】<br />\n日期 : 3月8日 (日)<br />\n時間 : 19:30 (20:09分默哀)<br />\n地點 : 將軍澳 尚十<br />\n*請自備蠟燭鮮花 , 及戴口罩<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D3018832514817307%26set%3Dgm.1240521269478455%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ee08cd2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3</a>"},{"pid":"034dd7702374632e2ecdea6a8f5105b97bf56fb9","tid":1911362,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"連港台呢種和理非都要打壓 仲好意思拎本基本法出黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd6dd224d2994ddc3a070b5bc7feba40216714b","tid":1911362,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"大氣頻道不是免費資源！本身港台節目得 4-5 點收視，轉新聞有 11-12 點收視，唔收返使用費即等於送錢比無線，分明利益輸送官商勾結。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf6792ce579fe0fae92c718cfc658ebe0fd499f","tid":1911362,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"點都要出聲"}]}